    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This enthusiast-spec example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox. The car benefits from critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis fatigue. The suspension retains its factory composure with recently refreshed control arm bushings and dampers, ensuring the M-variable differential lock translates power effectively through the corners. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the internals are robust, with a recent valve adjustment and Blackstone oil analysis confirming excellent engine health. This is a visceral, driver-centric machine ready for the open road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
