    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior presents beautifully with a deep luster, showing only the minor, unavoidable stone chips typical of a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment; the leather seats remain supple with no tears, and every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It features a robust engine that idles smoothly and a transmission that provides seamless gear changes. I have kept a comprehensive log of all scheduled maintenance, including recent fluid changes and a fresh set of high-performance tires. The brakes are firm, the suspension is quiet, and it drives straight and true. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy without immediate worry or expense.",
      "price": 34800.0,
